// InventoryModal.jsx
import React from 'react';
import {
    Dialog,
    DialogTitle,
    DialogContent,
    DialogActions,
    Button,
    TextField,
    MenuItem,
    Select,
    InputLabel,
    FormControl,
} from '@mui/material';

const InventoryModal = ({ isOpen, handlechange, products, toggleModal, addItemASLIst }) => {
    return (
        <Dialog open={isOpen} maxWidth="sm" fullWidth>
            <DialogTitle>Add New Purchase Entry</DialogTitle>
            <DialogContent dividers>

                <TextField fullWidth label="Inventory Name" margin="normal"
                    name="inventoryName"
                    onChange={(event) => handlechange(event)}
                    value={products.inventoryName}
                />

                <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal">
                    <InputLabel>Category</InputLabel>
                    <Select defaultValue=""
                        name='category'
                        onChange={(event) => handlechange(event)}
                        value={products.category}
                    >
                        <MenuItem value="Fertilizer">Fertilizer</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="Seeds">Seeds</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="pesticides">pesticides</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="Herbicides">Herbicides</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="pestFarming Tools">Farming Tools</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="GreenHouse shades and nets">GreenHouse shades and nets</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="GreenHouse shades and nets">Gardening ports</MenuItem>

                    </Select>
                </FormControl>


                <TextField fullWidth type="number" label="Price" margin="normal"
                    name='price'
                    onChange={(event) => handlechange(event)} value={products.price}
                />

                <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal">
                    <InputLabel>Unit</InputLabel>
                    <Select defaultValue=""
                        name='unit' onChange={(event) => handlechange(event)} value={products.unit}>
                        <MenuItem value="kg">kg</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="g">Gram (g)</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="litre">Litre (L)</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="pack">Pack</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="bottle">Bottle</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="ton">Ton</MenuItem>
                    </Select>
                </FormControl>

                <TextField fullWidth label="Source" margin="normal" name='source'
                    onChange={(event) => handlechange(event)} value={products.source}
                />

                <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal">
                    <InputLabel>Source Company</InputLabel>
                    <Select defaultValue=""
                        name='sourceCompany' onChange={(event) => handlechange(event)} value={products.sourceCompany}>
                        <MenuItem value="T.stanes&company">T.stanes&company</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="Madayikkan">Madayikkan</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="J J Tools">J J Tools</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="priya Agencies">priya Agencies</MenuItem>
                    </Select>
                </FormControl>

                <TextField fullWidth type="number" label="Available Quantity" margin="normal"
                    name='availableQuantity' onChange={(event) => handlechange(event)} value={products.availableQuantity} />

                <FormControl fullWidth margin="normal">
                    <InputLabel>Payment Status</InputLabel>
                    <Select defaultValue=""
                        name='paymentStatus' onChange={(event) => handlechange(event)} value={products.paymentStatus}
                    >
                        <MenuItem value="Paid">Paid</MenuItem>
                        <MenuItem value="Pending">Pending</MenuItem>

                    </Select>
                </FormControl>
            </DialogContent>
            <DialogActions>
                <Button onClick={toggleModal} color="inherit">Cancel</Button>
                <Button variant="contained" onClick={addItemASLIst}>Save</Button>
            </DialogActions>
        </Dialog>
    );
};

export default InventoryModal;
